David C Matthews wrote:
> I am sure this is simple to those who know, but *where* is the 
> starting solenoid on a '71 Camper?
it's above the transaxle on the passenger side.  just north of the 
tire.  at least that it where it's at on my 78.  the top bolt is 
accessed fromt he engine compartment though.  it's the 17mm on the right 
side just below the firewall.
